data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN - $270K @ 3.875%. SLASH YOUR INTEREST RATE IF YOU QUALIFY. CALL WITH QUESTIONS. Welcome to this Rare Single-Level Villa at Vibrant Architectural Palermo! This villa is just minutes from downtown Palm Springs and boasts two spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, separated by great room. The kitchen features stainless appliances, gas cooking and slab countertops that are visually pleasing and highly functional. The thoughtfully designed office nook serves as dedicated workspace and provides the perfect setting for productivity. Sealed concrete floors offer both durability and a modern aesthetic. Clerestory windows grace the living spaces, inviting in natural light, mountain views and enhancing the architectural beauty of the space. The villa soars with 12' 6" ceilings, giving every room an open and airy feel. Enjoy the outdoors in style with two private patios, perfect for morning coffee, evening relaxation, or entertaining guests. Covered carport next to front gate. You own the land. Gated community offers two pools, two spas, gym, and a recreational room. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional property your own. Contact us today to schedule a private showing.
